WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:04.356
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:13.560 --> 00:00:15.870
And all of you here are
in for a treat today.

00:00:15.870 --> 00:00:18.750
Sam Gralla, who I'm
very impressed with,

00:00:18.750 --> 00:00:21.900
is going to tell us about one
of the most amazing things

00:00:21.900 --> 00:00:24.600
that science has
done in a long time.

00:00:24.600 --> 00:00:28.320
And that's the measurement
