00:00:35.370 --> 00:00:39.810
But Sam is a theorist working
on gravitational physics

00:00:39.810 --> 00:00:42.420
and relativistic astrophysics.

00:00:42.420 --> 00:00:44.560
He's interested in the
strongest gravitational

00:00:44.560 --> 00:00:47.160
and electromagnetic
fields in the universe,

00:00:47.160 --> 00:00:49.410
which occur near black
holes and neutron stars.

00:00:49.410 --> 00:00:52.250
And you heard a little
bit about this last week.

00:00:52.250 --> 00:00:55.410
Sam applies techniques
from diverse communities,

00:00:55.410 --> 00:00:58.860
relativity, astrophysics,
